# FATHERHOOD TRANSITIONS MANUAL v1.0

**Subtitle:** How a father shifts states correctly in any moment.  

---

### Scenario A — When your son needs strength
**Transition:** ⟰ (rise into structure) | **Use:** Mirror + Governance Layer | **Outcome:** He feels safe.

### Scenario B — When your son needs connection
**Transition:** ⟱ (drop into presence) | **Use:** Praus + Bombadil | **Outcome:** He feels loved.

### Scenario C — When your son is overwhelmed
**Transition:** ⟡ (collapse story → core need) | **Outcome:** Emotional resolution.

### Scenario D — When your son is curious
**Transition:** ✦ (expand his world) | **Outcome:** Wonder grows.

### Scenario E — When your son is stuck
**Transition:** ↺ (reframe) | **Outcome:** Possibility reopens.

---

## The Fatherhood Invariant

**Your job is not to control his world. Your job is to control your transitions.**

This is how you become a stable, wise, loving father.
